\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb30 \strokec16 Banyue gains extra Sheer Force based on his Max HP, with every 1 point of Max HP increasing his Sheer Force by 0.1.\cb1 \
\cb30 All 
\f0\b \cf25 \strokec25 Fire DMG
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  Banyue deals is Sheer DMG, ignoring enemy DEF and using his Sheer Force stat as the DMG Multiplier.\cb1 \
\cb30 When Banyue enters the battlefield, he immediately recovers 60 Adrenaline. In Investigation Zone Mode, this effect can trigger once every 180s.\cb1 \
\cb30 Banyue can recover 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  through the following methods:\cb1 \
\cb30 Recover 0.5 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  for every point of Adrenaline consumed;\cb1 \
\cb30 Recover 4 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  upon activating 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Defensive Assist
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 ;\cb1 \
\cb30 Recover 4 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  when parrying an enemy with 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Dodge: Immovable Mountain
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , and recover 6 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  instead upon triggering a Perfect Block, up to once every 1s;\cb1 \
\cb30 Recover 4 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  upon triggering a 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Perfect Dodge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , up to once every 1s.\cb1 \
\cb30 Banyue can have up to 150 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . When he possesses at least 120 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Wrathful Fires
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , Banyue can enter the 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Visage of Wrath
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state by using 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Basic Attack: Immolate
