\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Visage of Wrath
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state, remove all 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Mountain's Might
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb30 When possessing 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Mountain's Might
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  in 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Visage of Wrath
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state, hold \cb1 \dn3 {{\NeXTGraphic Attachment.png \width320 \height320 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\cb30 \up0  to launch four different 
