\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 Did Banyue Shifu ever have any desires of his own? He runs a martial arts school in Failume Heights, apparently only because a certain grandmaster once suggested he open one.\cb1 \
\cb30 The school doesn't even have a name, he isn't looking for fame for fortune, and he's never once told his students to shout slogans about passing down his art.\cb1 \
\cb30 Only Banyue Shifu himself knows that the obsession called repentance burns that iron heart, day and night. A single mistake could send him spiralling.\cb1 \
\
\cb30 "Greed is like fire. When kept in check, it lights the way forward, but left unchecked, it burns you instead."\cb1 \
