\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 The students at the martial arts school had never seen Banyue Shifu lose his temper, let alone fly into a rage. Even with the dullest or most reckless students, he seemed endlessly patient. After all, how could a mountain ever grow angry? Its deep, immovable calm makes people almost forget the fury it can hold.\cb1 \
\cb30 But when it stirs with the wrath of the heavens, even the fiercest of beasts will tremble in fear.\cb1 \
\
\cb30 "Anger is like a blade \'97 keep it sheathed in daily life, lest it wound those around you."\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

