\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 Did you hear? There's a martial arts school up in the mountain taught by some big construct.\cb1 \
\cb30 The students there are no joke; they can even hold their own against Ethereals.\cb1 \
\cb30 Their iron-bodied Shifu often heads into the Hollows to help with rescues, too. Must be quite the martial arts master, huh?\cb1 \
\
\cb30 "I'm still just a clumsy student myself... Though you all call me 'Shifu,' it's you who have taught me what it means to be a person."\cb1 \
